  var cookieStr = window.document.cookie;

  if (!cookieStr) {

    return;

  }

  var cookieParts = cookieStr.split(/;\s/g);

  var strategyCookie;

  for (var i = 0, len = cookieParts.length; i < len; i++) {

    var values = cookieParts[i].match(/AB_STG=(.+)/i);
